  #read-the-paper
    .paper-icon
      a(href="http://vis.berkeley.edu/papers/videodigests/")
        img(src="http://192.241.199.43/img/paper.png")
    .paper-details
        h3
          a(href="http://vis.berkeley.edu/papers/videodigests/") Video Digests: A Browsable, Skimmable Format for Informational Lecture Videos
        p.authors Amy Pavel, Colorado Reed, Bjoern Hartmann, Maneesh Agrawala
        p.conference UIST 2014, October 2014


  #build-vd
    h3 Create a Video Digest
    ol
      li 
        a(href="http://vis.berkeley.edu/videodigests/signup") Create an account
        |   (contact [colorado at berkeley d0t edu] for beta access code)
      li
        a(href="http://vis.berkeley.edu/videodigests/editor") Upload video/transcript
      li After the video/transcript has processed, you will receive an email with a link to the video digest creator
      li Once finished editing the video digest, you can publish the results and share the link
